uot;/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote>你唔好笑人，你有冇聽過今個星期光頭頂講香港火紅年代的迷思；現在北美都有人講緊共產主義正在用左膠在北美開花&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我9錢十幾年前已經屌，左膠支膠乜膠都不過僭共諜！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係呢句，萬惡仁為首，西方尊崇既道德係支那永遠只會用作武器，唔會當乜價值！！！</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb7e016f92e7823fb80bdb19ba94fe77233a8d4","tid":987942,"uid":5220,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T21:45:32.000Z","msg":"加拿大真係好撚廢<br />\n<br />\n美國追住支那黎屌<br />\n支那竟然可以追住加拿大黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f4402501d6c4335de53d690d2e6493679f05d2","tid":987942,"uid":143183,"like":6,"dislike":53,"score":-47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T22:00:50.000Z","msg":"陶傑啲文章邏輯真係同响廟街講故佬同level<br />\n<br />\n香港人個腦退化到要睇飛機文  真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 反共 反左腦"},{"pid":"57964f16bd52b453cf6c0e1a9c7f610514ed91f8","tid":987942,"uid":61280,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T22:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陶傑啲文章邏輯真係同响廟街講故佬同level<br />\n<br />\n香港人個腦退化到要睇飛機文  真係&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt; <br />\n<br />\n利申 反共 反左腦</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你有腦夠IQ消化到先出黎乞啦6毛狗！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"803b17e8eefd9a6073ec7c875adba57d86e8f1c7","tid":987942,"uid":50310,"like